Included files:
    lab0.c: source module to copy stdin to stdout

    Makefile: Makefile that supports compilation with gcc with required flags,
    file cleaning, building distribution tarbell, smoke tests

    backtrace.png: gdb session showing seg fault with associated stack frame

    breakpoint.png: gdb session showing breakpoint and variable inspection

Smoke-test cases:
    test that input matches output
    test for correct exit codes
        normal execution exit(0)
        unrecognized argument exit(1)
        unable to open input file exit(2)
        unable to create output file exit(3)
        seg fault exit(4)

